        {
            "title": "滬深A股早市全程報升 滬指4000點得復失 券商股領跑",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內地股市今早跟隨外圍反彈，滬深兩市股指全程報升，券商股表現突出，首季盈利勝預期的中信証券(06030)A股(600030.SH)價量齊升。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中信証券官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20230828_FI_source-web_06030_CITIC_FB.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中信証券官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20230828_FI_source-web_06030_CITIC_FB.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中信証券官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上證綜指高開19點後反覆向上，初段低位3979點時也升13點，其後曾重越4000點，最高見4011點，升44點即暫時行人止步，後段逐漸回落至4000點之下；滬指中午收報3991點，升24點或0.63%，半日成交6206.24億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指則在甫開市即收復14000點，早市全程在萬四關之上波動，半日低位14095點時仍漲99點，高位14350點時升幅更達353點，其後升幅一直維持在200點以上；深指中午收報14239點，漲243點或1.74%，成交8825.73億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數也升53點或1.18%，收報4620點；創業板指數升87點或2.62%，報3410點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250407_FI_source-ap_China_Trump_Tariffs_25097181957222-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250407_FI_source-ap_China_Trump_Tariffs_25097181957222-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">企業陸續公布今年首季業績，中信証券於昨天收市後派發的季度成績表勝預期，非但推動該公司今早A、H齊漲，其他券商股同樣借勢炒上。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中信証券A股半日升7.04%，報25.85元，成交87.68億元，在滬市A股成交額榜上排第2位。廣發証券(01776)A股(000776.SZ)升3.86%，報18.84元；華泰證券(06886)A股(601688.SH)升3.68%，報18.59元；南華期貨(02691)A股(603093.SH)更在開市初段升約10%後封板，報19.31元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15855693-%e6%bb%ac%e6%b7%b1a%e8%82%a1%e6%97%a9%e5%b8%82%e5%85%a8%e7%a8%8b%e5%a0%b1%e5%8d%87-%e6%bb%ac%e6%8c%874000%e9%bb%9e%e5%be%97%e5%be%a9%e5%a4%b1-%e5%88%b8%e5%95%86%e8%82%a1%e9%a0%98%e8%b7%91",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-10.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-10 11:36:13",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "日本3月批發通脹按年升2.6% 高於預期 進口價格飆升7.9%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">日本央行數據顯示，3月份反映批發價格的國內企業物價指數(CGPI)按年升幅擴大至2.6%，高於市場預期的2.4%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：日本央行官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/bplib_20230710-144753_source-web_JCB_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：日本央行官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/bplib_20230710-144753_source-web_JCB_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：日本央行官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">若與2月份比較，指數則上升0.8%。數據顯示，企業正將金屬、化工及其他原材料成本上漲轉嫁予客户，而汽油、化工產品及金屬製品價格上升，是推動按月升幅的主要因素。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">至於上月進口價格指數，按年更大幅上升7.9%，升幅遠高於2月修正後的2.7%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">日本央行副總裁冰見野良在國會表示，央行在制定最恰當的貨幣政策時，將考慮如何穩定實現2%的通脹目標，並會關注中東局勢衝擊及經濟情況。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">他又指出，日本未陷入滯脹，通脹仍在大約2%徘徊，經濟增長率仍高於潛在水平，但警告若中東衝突持續，既拖累經濟又推高通脹，央行將面對兩難局面。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15855615-%e6%97%a5%e6%9c%ac3%e6%9c%88%e6%89%b9%e7%99%bc%e9%80%9a%e8%84%b9%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e5%8d%872-6-%e9%ab%98%e6%96%bc%e9%a0%90%e6%9c%9f-%e9%80%b2%e5%8f%a3%e5%83%b9%e6%a0%bc%e9%a3%86%e5%8d%877-9",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20231024_FI_source_licensed_JapanEco_shutterstock_704.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-10 11:36:13",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "日股半日升幅擴大至1.49%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">日股今早高開後穩步向上，日經平均指數中午收報56728點，升幅擴大至833點或1.49%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15855436-%e6%97%a5%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e5%8d%87%e5%b9%85%e6%93%b4%e5%a4%a7%e8%87%b31-49",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/20241203_FI_source-ap_Japan_Financial_Markets_-1-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-10 10:37:09",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "亞開行料中國今明兩年增長放緩至4.6%及4.5% 油價高企勢令通脹小幅回升",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">亞洲開發銀行今早發表區內最新經濟展望報告，當中預期中國今明兩年增長將分別放緩至4.6%及4.5%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240415_FI_source-ap_ChinaEco-2.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240415_FI_source-ap_ChinaEco-2.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">報告指出，中國經濟在強勁出口和韌性工業活動的支持下，於2025年實現5%的增長，但居民消費疲軟及房地產行業持續調整，未來仍拖累增長步伐。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">短期內，出口以及政府對戰略性產業和高技術領域的投資，仍是主要增長動力，在一定程度上對沖國內消費不振及中東衝突引發外需的不確定性。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">亞開行估計，受到中東衝突推高全球能源價格，再加上內地食品成本上漲、反內捲政策推進等因素疊加影響，預期中國通脹2026年將微升至0.6%，2027年或再升至1%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">報告又明言，現時經濟前景面臨的下行風險增加，若全球能源價格持續高企且供應鏈擾動不斷，或通過推高能源成本、阻斷供應鏈和貿易、收緊金融狀況以及削弱投資與消費情緒，壓抑經濟增長。中東衝突延宕帶來的生產成本上漲壓力及營商環境惡化，亦難免影響企業盈利，並對私人投資及消費信心產生負面作用。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15855233-%e4%ba%9e%e9%96%8b%e8%a1%8c%e6%96%99%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e4%bb%8a%e6%98%8e%e5%85%a9%e5%b9%b4%e5%a2%9e%e9%95%b7%e6%94%be%e7%b7%a9%e8%87%b34-6%e5%8f%8a4-5-%e6%b2%b9%e5%83%b9%e9%ab%98%e4%bc%81%e5%8b%a2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/static/20230718-default-feature-704x369.jpg",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-10 09:57:11",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "中國3 月CPI報1%  PPI轉正報0.5%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中國3月消費物價指數(CPI)升1%，上月為1.3% ; 生產者物價指數(PPI)升0.5%，上月為負0.9%。</p>\n</div>",
